4. The Municipal Accountant maintains subsidiary ledgers for accounts RPT Receivable and SET Receivable in accordance with Section 10 of the NGAS Manual for LGUs, Volume II.

72. The Municipal Accountant and Municipal Treasurer reconcile the difference between the RPT and SET Receivables account balances totaling ₱18,359,226.24 and henceforth, conduct periodic reconciliation, together with the Municipal Assessor, of the total collectibles from the Basic and Special Education Tax with the balances of the RPT Receivables and SET Receivables accounts to avoid accumulation of unreconciled differences;
